  342:             /**
  343:              * Defines a class for the given class loader.
  344:              *
  345:              * @param classLoader          The class loader for which a new class should be defined.
  346:              * @param name                 The binary name of the class that should be defined.
  347:              * @param binaryRepresentation The binary representation of the class.
  348:              * @param protectionDomain     The protection domain for the defined class.
  349:              * @return The defined, loaded class.
  350:              */
  351:             Class<?> defineClass(ClassLoader classLoader, String name, byte[] binaryRepresentation, @MaybeNull ProtectionDomain protectionDomain);
