3Ow3chqhr2GjvLSsyHt4OoH9IE=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Finalizing metadata instructions**\\n\\nI need to ensure that the instructions for the metadata are clear and concise. It’s good that there’s no reporter-provided missing metadata. However, I should mention that we didn’t add any metadata, and highlight that tests were not run as per the instruction. I’ll create a final summary that clearly lists the files involved and any changes made. It’s all about keeping everything organized and clear for easy reference!\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented targeted coverage work for the active class.\n\nChanged:\n- `tests/src/io.projectreactor.tools/blockhound/1.0.8.RELEASE/build.gradle`\n  - Added required `testImplementation 'io.projectreactor:reactor-core:3.2.5.RELEASE'`.\n  - Enabled `-Djava.security.manager=allow` for JVM tests on JDKs before 24 so the dispatcher security-manager initialization path can execute.\n\n- Added:\n  - `tests/src/io.projectreactor.tools/blockhound/1.0.8.RELEASE/src/test/java/io_projectreactor_tools/blockhound/ClassInjectorInnerUsingReflectionInnerDispatcherInnerUsingUnsafeOverrideTest.java`\n\nThe new test uses an isolated child-first class loader to force Byte Buddy’s shaded `ClassInjector.UsingReflection.Dispatcher.UsingUnsafeOverride` path by first initializing `ClassInjector.UsingUnsafe` with unsafe injection disabled, then exercising normal Byte Buddy class injection through the public shaded Byte Buddy API. It covers:\n- unsafe override dispatcher creation,\n- generated class definition,\n- package definition,\n- package fallback via `getPackage`,\n- class lookup,\n- security-manager initialization where supported.\n\nIt also catches Native Image unsupported dynamic-class-loading `Error`s with `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(...)`, as required.\n\nI did not run compile or tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0048ece5fd6cb84b016a291f4b3fd881978381e92f5ed9d975\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 639, "output": 857, "cacheRead": 61440, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 62936, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781079867223, "responseId": "resp_0048ece5fd6cb84b016a291f3bc8e0819790c0056b42594e21"}, "toolResults": []}
