throwUnlessUnsupportedFeatureError(error);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static URL[] classPathUrls() throws Exception {\n        String classPath = System.getProperty(\"java.class.path\", \"\");\n        if (classPath.isEmpty()) {\n            return new URL[0];\n        }\n        String[] entries = classPath.split(File.pathSeparator);\n        URL[] urls = new URL[entries.length];\n        for (int i = 0; i < entries.length; i++) {\n            urls[i] = new File(entries[i]).toURI().toURL();\n        }\n        return urls;\n    }","newText":"@SuppressWarnings({\"deprecation\", \"removal\"})\npublic class ClassInjectorInnerUsingReflectionInnerDispatcherInnerUsingUnsafeOverrideTest {\n    @Test\n    void injectsClassesThroughUnsafeOverrideDispatcher() {\n        try {\n            assertThat(new UsingUnsafeOverrideExercise().call()).isEqualTo(\"ok\");\n        } catch (Error error) {\n            rethrowUnlessUnsupportedFeatureError(error);\n        }\n    }"},{"oldText":"    private static final class ChildFirstByteBuddyClassLoader extends URLClassLoader {\n        private ChildFirstByteBuddyClassLoader(URL[] urls) {\n            super(urls, parentClassLoader());\n        }\n\n        private static ClassLoader parentClassLoader() {\n            return ClassInjectorInnerUsingReflectionInnerDispatcherInnerUsingUnsafeOverrideTest.class.getClassLoader();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        protected Class<?> loadClass(String name, boolean resolve) throws ClassNotFoundException {\n            synchronized (getClassLoadingLock(name)) {\n                Class<?> loadedClass = findLoadedClass(name);\n                if (loadedClass == null && shouldLoadChildFirst(name)) {\n                    try {\n                        loadedClass = findClass(name);\n                    } catch (ClassNotFoundException ignored) {\n                        loadedClass = null;\n                    }\n                }\n                if (loadedClass == null) {\n                